===Etymology===

From {{etyl|la|en}} {{term|tangentem|lang=la}}, the accusative of {{term|tangēns||touching|lang=la}} (in the phrase {{term||[[linea#Latin|līnea]] [[tango#Latin|tangēns]]|a touching line}}), the [[present participle]] of the verb {{term|tangō||touch|pos=verb|lang=la}}, from {{etyl|ine-pro|en}} {{term/t|ine-pro|*tag-}}, {{term/t|ine-pro|*taǵ-||to touch}}. Cognate with {{etyl|ang|-}} {{term|þaccian||to touch lightly, pat, stroke|lang=ang}}. More at {{l|en|thack}}, {{l|en|thwack}}.

